<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA54">
<l>tāḷāṟ cakaṭa mutaittup pakaṭuntik</l>
<l>kīḷā marutiṭaipōyk kēḻalāy – mīḷātu</l>
<l>maṇṇakalaṅ kīṇṭaṅkōr mātukanta mārpaṟku</l>
<l>peṇṇakalaṅ kātal peritu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To him whose chest a woman enjoys, there, after he, as a boar, had incurably</l>
<l>split the chest of the earth, after having gone between the myrobalan trees,</l>
<l>after pushing the bull [and] kicking the cart with [his] foot,</l>
<l>love [for him] is great in the chest of the woman.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
